ss=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pmi1665702770448.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pmi1665702770448.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pmi1665702770448.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pmi1665702770448\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This method activates the requested operation.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"pmi1665702770448__topic_d128762e1_d128763e1_d128764e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104pmi1665702770448_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"pmi1665702770448__codeblock_o5g_mwv_cwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">import com.rocketsoftware.uniface.jci.*;\n\nint accept() throws UnifaceException;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pmi1665702770448__section_sw1_4wv_cwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d267514e56\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"pmi1665702770448__parml_gbh_pwv_cwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">operationName</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Desired operation.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">parameters</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">An array of objects containing the parameters for\n                     <var class=\"keyword varname\">operationName</var>. <var class=\"keyword varname\">parameters[0]</var> is used for\n                  the return value. <var class=\"keyword varname\">parameters[1..n]</var> are used for the\n                     <var class=\"keyword varname\">operationName</var> parameters. </dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pmi1665702770448__section_xkl_swv_cwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d267514e97\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pmi1665702770448__p_d128777e1_d128778e1_d128779e1\">Returns the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> and\n            can throw one of the following exceptions:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"pmi1665702770448__ul_ahw_twv_cwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pmi1665702770448__li_d46472e1_d46473e1_d46474e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">NoSuchOperationException</span> when the operation is not provided. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pmi1665702770448__li_d46475e1_d46476e1_d46477e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">UnifaceException</span> when the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">activate</span> fails for\n               some other reason. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pmi1665702770448__section_b43_vwv_cwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d267514e127\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pmi1665702770448__p_d128783e1_d128784e1_d128785e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">UnifaceComponent</span> is the base class of the Java call-in. It provides\n            the classes that implement the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">activate</span> method.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pmi1665702770448__p_d128786e1_d128787e1_d128788e1\">Uniface generates methods that use the\n               <span class=\"keyword apiname\">activate</span> method when the Java (or JavaBean) wrappers are\n            generated.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pmi1665702770448__section_s3g_bxv_cwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d267514e148\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">quit</code> Method </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pmi1665702770448__p_d128792e1_d128793e1_d128794e1\">For example, the following Java code is generated\n            for the <code class=\"ph codeph\">quit</code> operation:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104pmi1665702770448_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"pmi1665702770448__codeblock_pjg_2xv_cwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">/** Operation quit. */\npublic int quit ()\nthrows UnifaceException {\nObject params[] = new Object[1];\nint status = activate (\"quit\", params);\nreturn status;\n}\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530963\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530963\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UnifaceComponent.activate Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 This method activates the requested operation. Explain this code import com.rocketsoftware.uniface.jci.*; int accept() throws UnifaceException; Copy Parameters operationName Desired operation. parameters An array of objects containing the parameters for operationName . parameters[0] is used for the return value. parameters[1..n] are used for the operationName parameters. Return Values Returns the value of $status and can throw one of the following exceptions: NoSuchOperationException when the operation is not provided. UnifaceException when the activate fails for some other reason. Description UnifaceComponent is the base class of the Java call-in. It provides the classes that implement the activate method. Uniface generates methods that use the activate method when the Java (or JavaBean) wrappers are generated. Example: quit Method For example, the following Java code is generated for the quit operation: Explain this code /** Operation quit. */ public int quit () throws UnifaceException { Object params[] = new Objec